&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.agou-ops.cn/others/image-20220406085729985.png" alt="image-20220406085729985">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>钉钉群聊机器人sample</title><link>https://agou-ops.cn/post/%E9%92%89%E9%92%89%E7%BE%A4%E8%81%8A%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BAsample/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Dec 2021 08:49:21 +0800</pubDate><author>suofeiyaxx@gmail.com (AGou-ops)</author><guid>https://agou-ops.cn/post/%E9%92%89%E9%92%89%E7%BE%A4%E8%81%8A%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BAsample/</guid><description>&lt;p>最近需要做一个钉钉群聊机器人，需求是：&lt;strong>艾特该机器人并发送相应关键字，机器人会进行相应的自动回复。&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
